1023
01:27:28,600 --> 01:27:30,431
You look lovely.

1024
01:27:30,520 --> 01:27:36,470
You've enchanted all Mexico
with your lovely eyes, warm and radiant.

1025
01:27:38,160 --> 01:27:39,434
Sandra.

1026
01:27:43,680 --> 01:27:44,829
Yesenia.

1027
01:27:45,480 --> 01:27:46,754
Welcome.

1028
01:27:47,120 --> 01:27:49,156
<i>You've worked hard to get here.</i>

1029
01:27:49,240 --> 01:27:51,071
