1030
01:27:51,720 --> 01:27:53,517
I must say,

1031
01:27:55,720 --> 01:27:57,312
you look lovely.

1032
01:28:00,160 --> 01:28:01,718
<i>You hear your name,</i>

1033
01:28:02,000 --> 01:28:04,195
