1040
01:28:35,560 --> 01:28:38,757
<i>You never frigging win.</i>

1041
01:28:39,560 --> 01:28:43,030
<i>It's funny because the best actress is me.</i>

1042
01:28:43,720 --> 01:28:44,994
<i>Best of them all.</i>

1043
01:28:45,240 --> 01:28:48,630
